Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.96,0:00:10.77,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,I love it when Princess Celestia comes to Ponyville!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.77,0:00:14.50,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,I got my hooves shined just like Rarity for the occasion. Ya like?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.50,0:00:16.03,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I certainly do!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.01,0:00:18.71,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised she's not here yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.71,0:00:20.71,Spike,,0,0,0,,I wonder what's taking so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.71,0:00:22.56,Twilight,,0,0,0,,And where are Applejack and Fluttershy?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.56,0:00:26.51,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy's detained helping Applejack with a mishap at Sweet Apple Acres.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.51,0:00:27.48,Rarity,,0,0,0,,They'll be along.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.48,0:00:30.14,Spike,,0,0,0,,But, I still don't get why the Princess would be so late.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.14,0:00:33.54,Twilight,,0,0,0,,She's bringing an important visitor. That could be part of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.54,0:00:36.44,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,A visitor who's important and slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.44,0:00:39.49,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's somepony so terribly important,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.49,0:00:42.91,Rarity,,0,0,0,,she still had many more terribly important things to do before she got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.97,0:00:48.25,Spike,,0,0,0,,Maybe the visitor has a deer antler, a goat leg, a bat wing, and a snake tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.46,0:00:50.28,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right. That's Discord.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.28,0:00:54.88,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Why in the wide-wide world of Equestria would Princess Celestia bring along someone like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.88,0:00:57.81,Spike,,0,0,0,,M-m-maybe you should ask... her!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.80,0:01:51.61,Twilight,,0,0,0,,With all due respect, Princess Celestia,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.61,0:01:54.49,Twilight,,0,0,0,,HOW COULD YOU BRING DISCORD HERE,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.53,0:01:56.53,Twilight,,0,0,0,,your Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.53,0:01:59.26,Celestia,,0,0,0,,I'm fully aware that the last time Discord was here
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.26,0:02:01.26,Celestia,,0,0,0,,he created serious havoc.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.73,0:02:06.92,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,If by "serious havoc" you mean turning Ponyville into the chaos capital of the world…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.92,0:02:09.77,Rarity,,0,0,0,,…and tricking us all into being the opposite of our true selves…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.77,0:02:12.62,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,…and making yummy delicious chocolate milk rain all over the place
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.62,0:02:15.84,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,without a single dollop of whipped cream to go with it anywhere in sight?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.84,0:02:18.12,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Not a single dollop!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.12,0:02:20.36,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Yes, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.36,0:02:25.29,Celestia,,0,0,0,,But I have use for Discord's magic if it can be reformed to serve good instead of evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.54,0:02:28.10,Celestia,,0,0,0,,This is why I've brought Discord here,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.10,0:02:32.42,Celestia,,0,0,0,,because I believe that you are the ponies who can help him do just that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.77,0:02:35.70,Spike,,0,0,0,,This will never work. This is a disaster! How do we ever control him?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.70,0:02:37.06,Spike,,0,0,0,,WE'RE DOOMED!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.06,0:02:40.01,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Need I remind you that you are the ponies who turned him back
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.01,0:02:42.16,Celestia,,0,0,0,,into stone like this in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.87,0:02:46.03,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I suppose we can just use the Elements of Harmony against him again
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.03,0:02:47.38,Twilight,,0,0,0,,if he gets out of hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.30,0:02:52.03,Spike,,0,0,0,,W-we probably need a volunteer to run away from here right away to get them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.03,0:02:53.06,Spike,,0,0,0,,I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.06,0:02:54.62,Celestia,,0,0,0,,No need, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.62,0:02:56.00,Celestia,,0,0,0,,I have them right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.00,0:02:59.56,Celestia,,0,0,0,,And I've cast the spell so Discord can't take them and hide them again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.51,0:03:03.18,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Now, where is Fluttershy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.18,0:03:06.61,Celestia,,0,0,0,,I believe she may know best how to begin reforming Discord.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.61,0:03:09.41,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.35,0:03:15.34,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,What's he going on about now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.34,0:03:16.06,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Good news!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.06,0:03:20.05,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Mr. Beaverton Beaverteeth has agreed to take the dam apart and move it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.05,0:03:21.95,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Well, it's about time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.95,0:03:25.50,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,My appletrees are so waterlogged I can practically hear them gargle!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.74,0:03:31.97,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,But he says first you have to apologize for calling him a nuisance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.97,0:03:35.32,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Apologize? He's lucky I don't call him a varmint!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.32,0:03:40.61,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Mr. Beaverton Beaverteeth! Such a language!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.12,0:03:43.59,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Fine, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.51,0:03:46.03,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.75,0:03:58.16,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Fluttershy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.16,0:04:00.06,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Don't know what I would've done without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.06,0:04:01.46,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Glad I could help.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.46,0:04:02.86,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Hey slackers!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.86,0:04:04.95,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Double-time it over to Ponyville, would ya?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.95,0:04:06.14,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,We're all waiting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.74,0:04:12.25,Celestia,,0,0,0,,I realize that this is a tall order.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.25,0:04:14.81,Celestia,,0,0,0,,But I wouldn't ask if I weren't confident you could get
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.81,0:04:17.69,Celestia,,0,0,0,,him to use magic obediently of his own free will.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.69,0:04:20.88,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,And you really think I'll know best how to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.98,0:04:22.97,Celestia,,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.48,0:04:29.24,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Now, I must return to Canterlot for Equestria's royal summit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.24,0:04:31.56,Celestia,,0,0,0,,You may release Discord when ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.64,0:04:41.41,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Okay, ponies. Guess it's time to get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.41,0:04:43.74,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Let's just hope this releasing spell works.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.74,0:04:45.33,Spike,,0,0,0,,Or let's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.33,0:04:48.75,Twilight,,0,0,0,,We best keep our elements on at all times until further notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.75,0:04:49.80,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Check!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.81,0:05:31.56,Discord,,0,0,0,,Well, it's about time somepony got me out of this prison block.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.73,0:05:33.62,Discord,,0,0,0,,What a relief!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.42,0:05:38.81,Twilight,,0,0,0,,What do you think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.24,0:05:42.82,Discord,,0,0,0,,Why, stretching, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.03,0:05:45.45,Discord,,0,0,0,,When you're a creature of chaos stone body suits
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.45,0:05:48.22,Discord,,0,0,0,,aren't your typical go-to fashion choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.37,0:05:56.34,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Make that bunny cute again! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.16,0:06:00.91,Discord,,0,0,0,,He's adorable the way he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.42,0:06:04.76,Discord,,0,0,0,,You know what else is adorable?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.76,0:06:08.00,Discord,,0,0,0,,You ponies truly believe that you can reform me,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.00,0:06:11.95,Discord,,0,0,0,,and that you're putting your faith in this one here to make it happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.30,0:06:15.81,Discord,,0,0,0,,Makes me want to pinch your little horsy cheeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.81,0:06:17.03,Twilight,,0,0,0,,How'd you know about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.03,0:06:21.49,Discord,,0,0,0,,Being turned to stone doesn't keep me from hearing every word Celestia says.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.49,0:06:24.93,Discord,,0,0,0,,Although, I admit, it makes rolling my eyes a challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.69,0:06:29.18,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Well, unless you want us to turn you back to stone,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.18,0:06:32.28,Twilight,,0,0,0,,you'll zap those animals back the way they were pronto!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.28,0:06:34.69,Discord,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't dare turn me back to stone
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.69,0:06:38.25,Discord,,0,0,0,,and risk disappointing your precious princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.28,0:06:40.28,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Try us, "Dip-cord"!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.30,0:06:44.25,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,You think you can treat poor defenceless animals like that and get away with it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.25,0:06:45.92,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,You go, Fluttershy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.02,0:06:49.66,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,You best watch your steps, buster, or I'll give you…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.66,0:06:51.21,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,The Stare!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.36,0:06:53.33,Discord,,0,0,0,,The Stare? Oh no, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.33,0:06:57.10,Discord,,0,0,0,,Not that! Anything but your disapproving eyeballs!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.36,0:07:04.26,Discord,,0,0,0,,Oh no! No-no-no-no, stop! No-no!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.16,0:07:06.02,Discord,,0,0,0,,I can't…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.66,0:07:10.36,Discord,,0,0,0,,Stop! I can't take it anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.36,0:07:14.01,Discord,,0,0,0,,I'll do whatever you say! Because…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.25,0:07:18.64,Discord,,0,0,0,,You're hilarious!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.42,0:07:22.47,Twilight,,0,0,0,,If it turns out we need to use our elements against you,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.47,0:07:26.24,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I'm sure we can convince Princess Celestia it was for a good reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.94,0:07:29.78,Discord,,0,0,0,,I suppose that's correct!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.53,0:07:44.14,Discord,,0,0,0,,Ooopsie…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.14,0:07:48.03,Discord,,0,0,0,,Well, it looks like I know where I'll be crashing...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.03,0:07:51.15,Discord,,0,0,0,,while I'm being "reformed"…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.16,0:07:53.95,Discord,,0,0,0,,With you, Fluttershy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.21,0:07:58.20,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Oh dear…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.99,0:08:06.05,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,He may be horrible, but that doesn't mean we have to act the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.05,0:08:08.07,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,We should at least try to be hospitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.34,0:08:12.50,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,You don't mind giving up your favorite spot on the couch, do you,  Angel Bunny?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.92,0:08:18.17,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry about Angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.17,0:08:19.36,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.36,0:08:22.49,Discord,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes. Thank you, Fluttershy, for your concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.49,0:08:25.58,Discord,,0,0,0,,If only your pony friends could be as considerate...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.58,0:08:27.22,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Don't listen to him, Fluttershy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.22,0:08:30.40,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,He's just trying to drive a wedge between us, like he always does.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.40,0:08:35.59,Discord,,0,0,0,,Now why in the world would I ever try to do a thing like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.59,0:08:40.02,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,So we can't unite and use the Elements of Harmony against you, that's why!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.02,0:08:42.47,Discord,,0,0,0,,I never thought of that…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.47,0:08:44.15,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,You big liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.15,0:08:45.90,Discord,,0,0,0,,Now, look who's a liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.90,0:08:49.33,Discord,,0,0,0,,Anyone can plainly see that I'm not big at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.66,0:08:54.64,Discord,,0,0,0,,Oops.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.27,0:08:58.75,Discord,,0,0,0,,There, all better.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.88,0:09:03.47,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I can't watch...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.47,0:09:04.71,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,We'll be outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.19,0:09:08.77,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You sure you're okay with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.77,0:09:10.54,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I know it's not gonna be easy,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.54,0:09:12.84,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,but Princess Celestia's counting on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.00,0:09:15.72,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,And... I think I actually know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.72,0:09:16.47,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.47,0:09:19.13,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I think the key is to befriend him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.13,0:09:21.49,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Being kind to him and letting him be my house guest
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.49,0:09:23.82,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,is probably the best way to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.82,0:09:25.52,Twilight,,0,0,0,,And you really think that'll work?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.52,0:09:27.01,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I think it's worth a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.01,0:09:29.05,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Okay, but if you need us,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.05,0:09:30.90,Twilight,,0,0,0,,all you need to do is whisper "help",
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.90,0:09:33.21,Twilight,,0,0,0,,and we'll be back here with our Elements.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.21,0:09:36.77,Twilight,,0,0,0,,So watch that goat-legged step of yours, pal!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.50,0:09:39.09,Discord,,0,0,0,,Wh-what?! Look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.09,0:09:41.90,Discord,,0,0,0,,I'm practically reformed already.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.38,0:09:46.90,Rarity,,0,0,0,,She's really alright with him staying there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.90,0:09:48.05,Twilight,,0,0,0,,That's what she said.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.05,0:09:50.64,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Personally, I think we should come up with a backup plan
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.64,0:09:53.78,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,in case this whole "befriending" business doesn't work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.78,0:09:57.01,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash is right. This is Discord we are talking about, girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.01,0:10:00.89,Rarity,,0,0,0,,It wouldn't be a bad idea to have another trick upon our sleeves.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.30,0:10:03.97,Twilight,,0,0,0,,And I think I know just the trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.47,0:10:05.94,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Discord?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.94,0:10:08.62,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Oh, there you are. Listen, Discord,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.62,0:10:12.20,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I just wanna make sure you know that if there's anything I can do, just…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.70,0:10:15.31,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Are you eating…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.31,0:10:16.58,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,paper?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.11,0:10:20.17,Discord,,0,0,0,,Am I? How odd of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.79,0:10:23.39,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Well, um…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.39,0:10:25.21,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I'm just heading out, so,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.21,0:10:27.82,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,you just make yourself at home while I'm gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.71,0:10:31.43,Discord,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye and have a nice time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.43,0:10:35.33,Discord,,0,0,0,,Everything is fine here. Bye-bye. Bye-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.96,0:10:39.06,Discord,,0,0,0,,You like carrots, Angel?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.72,0:10:42.78,Discord,,0,0,0,,I'm playing your owner for a fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.70,0:10:45.37,Discord,,0,0,0,,How do you like them carrots?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.22,0:10:53.35,Twilight,,0,0,0,,That's weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.35,0:10:55.54,Twilight,,0,0,0,,The spell I had in mind isn't in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.54,0:10:58.18,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Spike, where are the other books I asked you to pull?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.18,0:10:59.41,Spike,,0,0,0,,Right here, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.41,0:11:02.42,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I really want to have a reforming spell up and running pronto.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.42,0:11:06.01,Spike,,0,0,0,,But what if he makes the Elements of Harmony disappear like he did last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.01,0:11:08.91,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Princess Celestia casted a spell protecting them, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.61,0:11:11.38,Spike,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.38,0:11:14.64,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Princess Celestia didn't cast a spell protecting our books!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.64,0:11:16.91,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Everywhere I thought I'd find the reforming spell…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.35,0:11:24.69,Discord,,0,0,0,,Are you sure this isn't overdoing it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.69,0:11:26.90,Discord,,0,0,0,,You said to make myself like at home while you were gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.90,0:11:29.48,Discord,,0,0,0,,But I wouldn't want to overstep my bounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.35,0:11:32.65,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I did say that, so…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.65,0:11:34.51,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,if this makes you more comfortable…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.51,0:11:37.14,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,by all means, please feel free.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.14,0:11:39.30,Discord,,0,0,0,,Oh, well, it does, very much so.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.30,0:11:43.37,Discord,,0,0,0,,You're so very kind, my dear Fluttershy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.37,0:11:45.83,Discord,,0,0,0,,I always knew, that you'd be the understanding one,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.83,0:11:48.86,Discord,,0,0,0,,not like those nasty friends of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.35,0:11:51.09,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,My friends aren't nasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.09,0:11:53.09,Discord,,0,0,0,,Of course you'd say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.09,0:11:56.37,Discord,,0,0,0,,It's just goes to show how understanding you truly are.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.32,0:12:00.98,Discord,,0,0,0,,You know, I think Princess Celestia is right
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.98,0:12:04.32,Discord,,0,0,0,,when she singles you out as the one, who could reform me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.80,0:12:06.11,Discord,,0,0,0,,You're off to such a good start
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.11,0:12:10.08,Discord,,0,0,0,,I'm seriously considering actually being reformed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.66,0:12:11.74,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.74,0:12:13.49,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy, can you hear me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.49,0:12:15.56,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Goodness! I hear Twilight!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.46,0:12:20.34,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.34,0:12:21.24,Twilight,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.24,0:12:22.17,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.17,0:12:24.85,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,We're fine, everything is going great.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.85,0:12:26.37,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Isn't it, Angel?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.49,0:12:31.44,Twilight,,0,0,0,,We've come to get you away from Discord,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.44,0:12:32.84,Twilight,,0,0,0,,he is just terrible and,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.84,0:12:35.36,Twilight,,0,0,0,,from the looks of it, completely out of control!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.36,0:12:36.79,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Oh, but you're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.79,0:12:39.57,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,We're making great progress!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.57,0:12:41.01,Spike,,0,0,0,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.57,0:12:41.01,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.01,0:12:45.09,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I'm earning his trust by giving him a little space to be himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.09,0:12:46.52,Spike,,0,0,0,,Hate to break it to ya,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.52,0:12:48.67,Spike,,0,0,0,,but he used this "space to be himself"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.67,0:12:51.43,Spike,,0,0,0,,to tear all the reforming spells from the library!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.43,0:12:53.95,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,That does explain the paper eating…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.95,0:12:55.88,Twilight,,0,0,0,,He ate them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.39,0:12:59.19,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,We aren't gonna need a spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.19,0:13:01.75,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,He's already really considering being reformed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.75,0:13:03.00,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,He said so.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.00,0:13:04.45,Twilight,,0,0,0,,And you believed him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.45,0:13:06.00,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,If I'm going to be his friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.00,0:13:08.60,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I'd start with giving him the benefit of the doubt!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.60,0:13:09.49,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Tell you what,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.49,0:13:12.20,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,bring all the ponies over for dinner party this evening,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.20,0:13:15.44,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,and I'll bet his manners will have really improved by then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.12,0:13:20.52,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I'll even get him to put the cottage back on the ground first.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.92,0:13:23.89,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Alright, dinner it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.00,0:13:30.63,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I can't believe we're having a dinner party with Discord.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.63,0:13:32.90,Rarity,,0,0,0,,This evening is sure to be a disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.90,0:13:35.94,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Glad I didn't bother wearing my fanciest outfit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.94,0:13:39.99,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy thinks this is the way to reform Discord and asked us to give it a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.78,0:13:43.16,Discord,,0,0,0,,Oh, our pony guests!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.01,0:13:47.74,Discord,,0,0,0,,We're so delighted that you've come.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.87,0:13:51.36,Discord,,0,0,0,,Please do come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.68,0:13:56.47,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,See what a beautiful job he did helping?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.47,0:13:59.41,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Discord set the entire table himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.41,0:14:01.41,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I'm so proud!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.16,0:14:04.57,Discord,,0,0,0,,May I take your…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.57,0:14:06.78,Discord,,0,0,0,,hats, ladies?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.08,0:14:08.87,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Hang on to your Elements, girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.87,0:14:10.87,Twilight,,0,0,0,,It's gonna be a bumpy night.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.41,0:14:13.69,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,As you all know,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.69,0:14:18.53,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Princess Celestia hopes we'll help Discord to use his magic for good instead of evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.98,0:14:22.05,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Pinkie Pie, care for some gravy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.05,0:14:23.13,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,You bet!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.13,0:14:24.98,Discord,,0,0,0,,Allow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.77,0:14:30.77,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,What a cute little gravy boat you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.77,0:14:32.97,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Yes, you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.45,0:14:37.98,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,That's one creepy little gravy boat, if you ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.98,0:14:39.72,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on now, Dashie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.72,0:14:41.99,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,You're not even giving this a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.03,0:14:44.71,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Hey, that's hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.71,0:14:47.33,Discord,,0,0,0,,Whoops, I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.33,0:14:48.85,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,He did that on purpose!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.85,0:14:50.81,Discord,,0,0,0,,Oh, well, I don't know about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.81,0:14:52.32,Discord,,0,0,0,,Mistakes happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.32,0:14:54.23,Discord,,0,0,0,,Oh, look, everypony!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.23,0:14:56.39,Discord,,0,0,0,,Dancing candles!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.99,0:15:00.79,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I'm not falling for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.79,0:15:03.28,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Discord's just trying to distract us from…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.88,0:15:06.68,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Hey, knock it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.68,0:15:08.56,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I suppose, that's another "mistake"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.56,0:15:11.56,Discord,,0,0,0,,No, I think you just made them mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.56,0:15:13.38,Twilight,,0,0,0,,There's something fishy going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.29,0:15:17.25,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Discord!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.25,0:15:20.31,Discord,,0,0,0,,Well, it's hardly my fault if the soup tureen finds the term
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.31,0:15:23.54,Discord,,0,0,0,,"something fishy" to be offensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.54,0:15:24.17,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Not the dress!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.17,0:15:25.36,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Not the dress!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.36,0:15:28.14,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,That tureen is only doing what you're making it do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.14,0:15:30.78,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Now let's not jump to any conclusions.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.59,0:15:33.89,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy, can't you see what he's doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.89,0:15:38.58,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,He's playing innocent with you so you'll never agree to use the Elements of Harmony against him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.49,0:15:40.31,Discord,,0,0,0,,Oh, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.31,0:15:42.70,Discord,,0,0,0,,That's a bit harsh, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.47,0:15:46.63,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,You see what I'm saying, right, Fluttershy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.52,0:15:48.61,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.61,0:15:49.94,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,You know, what I see?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.94,0:15:52.34,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I see that Discord's far from perfect,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.34,0:15:55.01,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,but I also see none of you giving him a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.01,0:15:55.97,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.97,0:15:57.43,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,What's gotten into you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.43,0:15:59.66,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Why do you keep cutting him so much slack?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.66,0:16:03.19,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Because that's what friends do!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.76,0:16:05.99,Discord,,0,0,0,,We're friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.99,0:16:07.41,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Why, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.41,0:16:11.40,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I can't remember my house ever been this lively before you came along.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.11,0:16:14.17,Discord,,0,0,0,,Well, I…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.17,0:16:16.42,Discord,,0,0,0,,I never really had a friend before.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.42,0:16:18.01,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Well, now you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.64,0:16:25.44,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,And now it is not a good time, Angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.44,0:16:27.21,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,We're having a dinner party.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.21,0:16:28.20,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.20,0:16:30.18,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I think he's trying to tell us something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.52,0:16:33.58,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Apple!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.97,0:16:35.18,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Applejack!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.99,0:16:41.78,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Sweet Apple Acres?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.52,0:16:44.34,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Flooding at Sweet Apple Acres!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.34,0:16:47.08,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,And we all know, who's behind that now, don't we?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.08,0:16:47.93,Discord,,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.93,0:16:48.93,Discord,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.51,0:16:51.20,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Oh, give it a rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.20,0:16:54.73,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,What do you think of your friend now, Fluttershy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.71,0:17:02.96,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I've never seen a flooding this bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.96,0:17:04.76,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,They've built dams around here before,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.76,0:17:06.25,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,but never like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.25,0:17:07.39,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.01,0:17:10.91,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Such language!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.91,0:17:12.64,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,It's no use,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.64,0:17:15.00,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,they don't listen to a word I say!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.00,0:17:17.42,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,You see Discord's behind all this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.42,0:17:19.19,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Well, of course I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.19,0:17:21.75,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Do you all think I'm a silly, gullible fool?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.75,0:17:24.35,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Only in the sense of being silly and gullible...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.26,0:17:24.15,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.66,0:17:25.85,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Uh, no, not exactly…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.54,0:17:28.45,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I've just been trying to gain his friendship any way I can,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.45,0:17:31.11,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,so he'd come to trust and listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.11,0:17:33.02,Discord,,0,0,0,,Hey there, Fluttershy, you want a turn?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.02,0:17:35.14,Discord,,0,0,0,,The water's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.94,0:17:38.07,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Time to see if it worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.49,0:17:42.64,Discord,,0,0,0,,Huh, there you are. A sight for sore eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.64,0:17:43.74,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,As you can see,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.74,0:17:46.85,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,there's a big mess down here at Sweet Apple Acres.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.85,0:17:49.17,Discord,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes. Awful business, that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.12,0:17:51.72,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,It is awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.72,0:17:53.28,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,This is Applejack's home
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.28,0:17:55.77,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,and it's being destroyed by innocent creatures who
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.77,0:17:59.64,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,would never be acting this way if it weren't for your reckless behavior!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.30,0:18:02.41,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,You need to fix this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.21,0:18:04.52,Discord,,0,0,0,,What? Yes. Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.52,0:18:08.21,Discord,,0,0,0,,I will fix it. I only ask one thing in return…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.21,0:18:09.11,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.11,0:18:13.34,Discord,,0,0,0,,I ask that you never use your Element of Harmony against me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.47,0:18:16.15,Discord,,0,0,0,,As a sign of our friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.33,0:18:25.06,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I will never use my Element of Harmony against you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.85,0:18:27.19,Discord,,0,0,0,,Excellent!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.68,0:18:32.20,Discord,,0,0,0,,There! Much better!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.20,0:18:37.63,Discord,,0,0,0,,I do prefer ice-skating to water-skiing, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.81,0:18:41.16,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Discord!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.16,0:18:43.26,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,That's not fixing it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.73,0:18:46.88,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Why, I oughta!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.88,0:18:48.06,Discord,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.54,0:18:51.04,Discord,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, pal?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.04,0:18:52.60,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Don't call me your pal!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.79,0:18:55.36,Discord,,0,0,0,,Come skating with me
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.36,0:18:58.04,Discord,,0,0,0,,and we'll let the bygones be bygones.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.57,0:19:03.51,Spike,,0,0,0,,Here you go, Fluttershy, game on!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.51,0:19:06.18,Twilight,,0,0,0,,He fixes it or he goes back to being stone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.18,0:19:08.45,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Princess Celestia will understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.76,0:19:16.18,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I made a promise not to use my Element against him
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.18,0:19:17.90,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I'm going to keep it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.34,0:19:24.45,Discord,,0,0,0,,You see,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.45,0:19:27.48,Discord,,0,0,0,,she wants to have fun with me, because we're friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.48,0:19:29.58,Discord,,0,0,0,,She can't use the Elements against me, because
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.58,0:19:31.35,Discord,,0,0,0,,we're friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.35,0:19:34.00,Discord,,0,0,0,,I'm free forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.87,0:19:38.32,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Not! Your! Friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.16,0:19:40.53,Discord,,0,0,0,,Who cares.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.53,0:19:43.22,Discord,,0,0,0,,I can do whatever I want, whenever I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.22,0:19:44.61,Discord,,0,0,0,,I'm Discord,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.61,0:19:46.63,Discord,,0,0,0,,the Master of Chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.57,0:19:49.63,Discord,,0,0,0,,You think you can boss Discord around?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.63,0:19:52.57,Discord,,0,0,0,,You think I'm just going to turn all this back
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.57,0:19:54.26,Discord,,0,0,0,,because you say so?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.26,0:19:58.38,Discord,,0,0,0,,Because if I don't, I'll lose the one friend I ever had?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.82,0:20:08.64,Discord,,0,0,0,,Well played, Fluttershy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.26,0:20:10.60,Discord,,0,0,0,,Well played.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.40,0:20:31.21,Discord,,0,0,0,,I liked it better my way, but,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.21,0:20:32.76,Discord,,0,0,0,,I guess, when you're friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.76,0:20:36.46,Discord,,0,0,0,,you can't always have things exactly your way all the time, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.62,0:20:42.12,Discord,,0,0,0,,Yes, Princess, I'm
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.12,0:20:44.09,Discord,,0,0,0,,ready to use my magic for good,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.09,0:20:45.76,Discord,,0,0,0,,instead of evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.76,0:20:47.64,Discord,,0,0,0,,Most of the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.64,0:20:50.25,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Congratulations on your success, ponies.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.25,0:20:53.75,Celestia,,0,0,0,,I definitely sense a big change in Discord.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.38,0:20:57.30,Celestia,,0,0,0,,I'll leave the Elements of Harmony with you, Twilight,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.30,0:20:58.56,Celestia,,0,0,0,,just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.55,0:21:01.58,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You were right,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.58,0:21:05.47,Twilight,,0,0,0,,when you said Fluttershy would be the one to find a way to reform Discord.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.47,0:21:07.26,Twilight,,0,0,0,,By treating Discord as a friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.26,0:21:09.43,Twilight,,0,0,0,,she got him to realize that friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.43,0:21:11.53,Twilight,,0,0,0,,was actually important to him
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.53,0:21:15.03,Twilight,,0,0,0,,and something that once he had, he didn't want to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.75,0:21:16.78,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Go on,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.78,0:21:18.30,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.75,0:21:20.62,Discord,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.62,0:21:22.29,Discord,,0,0,0,,Friendship is magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.63,0:21:25.65,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,See,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.65,0:21:29.82,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,he can be a real sweetheart once you get to know him.
